DocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527681\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527681\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fvf1665702683945.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fvf1665702683945.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fvf1665702683945.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fvf1665702683945\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__callfieldtrigger_211120\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Explicitly calls a detail, help, menu, or an interactive trigger on a field.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__topic_d69941e1_d69942e1_d69943e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104fvf1665702683945_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__codeblock_brv_bvz_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">callfieldtrigger  TriggerName,  FieldName</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__section_w1381ab1b7b5_w1382ab1b7_w1383ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__p_d69947e1_d69948e1_d69949e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">callfieldtrigger \"detail\", FIELD1</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__topic_d45847e1_d45848e1_d45849e1_d45850e1_d45851e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d768791e74\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6143e1_d6144e1_d6145e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6143e1_d6144e1_d6145e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6143e1_d6144e1_d6145e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6143e1_d6144e1_d6145e1__entry__3\">\n Values\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6143e1_d6144e1_d6145e1__entry__4\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6143e1_d6144e1_d6145e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">TriggerName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6143e1_d6144e1_d6145e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6143e1_d6144e1_d6145e1__entry__3\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">detail</code>,  <code class=\"ph codeph\">help</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">menu</code>, or\n                        the name of a field-level interactive trigger that has no\n                        parameters.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6143e1_d6144e1_d6145e1__entry__4\">\n Field-level trigger to call\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6143e1_d6144e1_d6145e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6143e1_d6144e1_d6145e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6143e1_d6144e1_d6145e1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6143e1_d6144e1_d6145e1__entry__4\">\n Field of the trigger to be called\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__topic_d45852e1_d45853e1_d45854e1_d45855e1_d45856e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d768791e163\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6146e1_d6147e1_d6148e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values Returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6146e1_d6147e1_d6148e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6146e1_d6147e1_d6148e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6146e1_d6147e1_d6148e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">&gt;=0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6146e1_d6147e1_d6148e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Success. Value returned by the trigger.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6146e1_d6147e1_d6148e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">&lt;0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6146e1_d6147e1_d6148e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6149e1_d6150e1_d6151e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned by\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">calltrigger</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6149e1_d6150e1_d6151e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6149e1_d6150e1_d6151e1__entry__2\">\n Error Constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6149e1_d6150e1_d6151e1__entry__3\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6149e1_d6150e1_d6151e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1101</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6149e1_d6150e1_d6151e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;PROCERR_FIELD&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6149e1_d6150e1_d6151e1__entry__3\">Specified field does not exist. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6149e1_d6150e1_d6151e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1120</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6149e1_d6150e1_d6151e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;PROCERROR_OPERATION&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6149e1_d6150e1_d6151e1__entry__3\">Specified trigger does not exist on field level\n                        or on entity level. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6149e1_d6150e1_d6151e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1123</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6149e1_d6150e1_d6151e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;PROCERR_NPARAMETERS&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fvf1665702683945__table_d6149e1_d6150e1_d6151e1__entry__3\">Specified trigger has one or more parameters. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__topic_d45857e1_d45858e1_d45859e1_d45860e1_d45861e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d768791e347\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__topic_d45862e1_d45863e1_d45864e1_d45865e1_d45866e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d768791e356\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__p_d69965e1_d69966e1_d69967e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">callfieldtrigger</span> statement explicitly calls the named trigger for the specified field. Only triggers that have no implicit processing can be called.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__p_d69968e1_d69969e1_d69970e1\">If the trigger is not defined at field level, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">callfieldtrigger</span> statement falls back to the same trigger on entity level. For the menu trigger, it can also fall back to the component- or application-level trigger.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fvf1665702683945__p_d69971e1_d69972e1_d69973e1\">For some DSP widgets it is possible for the user to trigger an event, such as onclick, ondblclick, onblur, and so on. DSP widgets can use these to a call a trigger on the field to which the widget is bound.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fcj1719477302864.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Triggers in Dynamic Server Pages</a><p>Dynamic server pages (DSPs) have system triggers that are executed on the server, and client-side web triggers that are executed in the browser.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527681\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527681\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "callfieldtrigger Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Explicitly calls a detail, help, menu, or an interactive trigger on a field. Explain this code callfieldtrigger TriggerName, FieldName Copy Example: callfieldtrigger \"detail\", FIELD1 Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Values Description TriggerName String detail , help , menu , or the name of a field-level interactive trigger that has no parameters. Field-level trigger to call FieldName String Field of the trigger to be called Return Values Table 2. Values Returned in $status Value >=0 Success. Value returned by the trigger. <0 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned by calltrigger Value Error Constant Meaning -1101 <PROCERR_FIELD> Specified field does not exist. -1120 <PROCERROR_OPERATION> Specified trigger does not exist on field level or on entity level. -1123 <PROCERR_NPARAMETERS> Specified trigger has one or more parameters. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The callfieldtrigger statement explicitly calls the named trigger for the specified field. Only triggers that have no implicit processing can be called. If the trigger is not defined at field level, the callfieldtrigger statement falls back to the same trigger on entity level. For the menu trigger, it can also fall back to the component- or application-level trigger. For some DSP widgets it is possible for the user to trigger an event, such as onclick, ondblclick, onblur, and so on. DSP widgets can use these to a call a trigger on the field to which the widget is bound. Related Links Triggers in Dynamic Server Pages Dynamic server pages (DSPs) have system triggers that are executed on the server, and client-side web triggers that are executed in the browser. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}